"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-team-usa-olympics-roster-predicting-team-starting-lineup-rotations-for-paris-01hqs4mve18y\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Coming off the heels of a disappointing result in the 2023FIBA Basketball World Cup, Team USA is constructing a Monstars-esque roster in their pursuit of a gold medal at the 2024 ParisOlympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 85, \"end\": 93, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 1.1058555643403664e-11, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While international talent continues to improve, the American national team failed to medal at the FIBA World Cup for the second consecutive tournament in large part due to the lack of star power.\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999997171471, \"rank\": 2.8276000305722135e-10, \"text\": \"American national team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA was littered with talented players and young All-Stars this past summer, but they lacked a veteran superstar(s).\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 392, \"end\": 400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 1.1058555643403664e-11, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http:/