": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vardon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Vardon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Vardon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Moreover, Anthony Edwards (Minnesota Timberwolves) and Tyrese Haliburton (Indiana Pacers) are \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cunder strong consideration\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d to be the only two players from the 2023 FIBA World Cup roster to represent the USA at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.8852849693611267, \"rank\": 0.1266663796691376, \"text\": \"Anthony Edwards\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\"}, {\"begin\": 1295, \"end\": 1304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Timberwolves\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.028668870665569e-17, \"text\": \"Minnesota\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Timberwolves\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Timberwolves\"}, {\"begin\": 1305, \"end\": 1317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Timberwolves\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.58584180720403e-33, \"text\": \"Timberwolves\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Timberwolves\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Timberwolves\"}, {\"begin\": 1323, \"end\": 1340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyrese_Haliburton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tyrese Haliburton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyrese_Haliburton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyrese_Haliburton\"}, {\"begin\": 1342, \"end\": 1356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Pacers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2537942066030133e-54, \"text\": \"Indiana Pacers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Pacers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Pacers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The duo of Charania and Vardon also highlight Bam Adebayo (Miami Heat) and Anthony Davis (Lakers) as \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cstrong candidates.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  With 11 roster spots potentially locked up, that leaves one opening remaining, but for who?\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1527, \"end\": 1533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Vardon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vardon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Vardon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Vardon\"}, {\"begin\": 1553, \"end\": 1560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bam_Adebayo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8390369987732089e-28, \"text\": \"Adebayo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bam_Adebayo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bam_Adebayo\"}, {\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Davis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.987625473780599e-45, \"text\": \"Anthony Davis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Davis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Davis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Until that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s sorted out, let\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s try to predict Team USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s starting lineup and depth chart with the 11-man rotation reportedly at our disposal as things stand.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\